data.description: THINK YOU CAN’T AFFORD EAST COBB??? THINK AGAIN!!! Here’s a rare find in the Falcon Wood swim-tennis community! A 4-bedroom 2.5 bath Classic Georgian Country Style Home – priced $70,000 under market because it just needs a bit of TLC. In the last few years all the major work has been done: the HVAC System (4 years old), Hot Water Heater (2 years old), and roof (1 year old!) Now all it needs is the “HGTV” fashion styling that makes a home pretty and cozy and warm! Sit out on your sweet covered “rocking chair” porch and waive to the neighbors. Have morning coffee in the peaceful quiet of your screened covered rear porch! Kids or pets (or both if you have them) can romp and play in the huge, privacy-fenced rear yard! This home is possibly the best deal in East Cobb! A great location – so close to shopping and WOW restaurants! Top rated Cobb schools! One of the best locations in Marietta - and ready to perk up to be the nicest home in town! This home comes with our exclusive “Love Your Home Guarantee!”* Plus, VIP Buyers with a home to sell – buy this one and we’ll buy yours!*  EVERY DAY OPEN TO THE PUBLIC – CALL FOR DETAILS!
